  "title": "Schedule | Plan Your Visit Now — Kane County Cougars",
  "textSample": "By using this website, you agree to our use of cookies. We use cookies to provide you with a great experience and to help our website run effectively.\n\nAccept\n\nJoin our mailing lists to be the first to hear about the Cougars, and receive special offers!\n\nSkip to Content\nTickets and Schedule\nKnow Before You Go\nNorthwestern Medicine Field\nNews\nTeam\nShop\nBuy Tickets\nAdd to Google Calendar\nPrint Schedule\nPromotions\n\n34W002 Cherry Lane\nGeneva, IL 60134\n\ninfo@kccougars.com\n(630) 232-8811\n\nJob Opportunities\n\nIn-Season Office Hours (Non-Game Days) \n\n10:00 AM to 5:00 PM\n\nOffice Hours (Game Days) \n\nM to F 10:00 AM to End of 6th inning\n\nWeekend Day Game 10:00 AM to End of 6th inning\n\nWeekend Night Game 11:00 AM to End of 6th inning\n\nSingle Game Tickets On Sale Now!\n\nPurchase your Cougars 2026 single-game tickets now! We can’t wait to see you at the ballpark! #choosecougs\n\nBuy Tickets",
